.Dd September 23, 2005
.Dt PAM_LCTX 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm pam_lctx
.Nd "Login Context PAM module"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Op Ar service-name
.Ar module-type
.Ar control-flag
.Pa pam_lctx
.Op Ar options
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The Login Context session service module for PAM,
.Nm
provides functionality for only one PAM category:
session management.
In terms of the
.Ar module-type
parameter, this is the
.Dq Li session
feature.
.Pp
The module will create a Login Context which will be inherited
by all subsequent processes created by the login.
.Pp
The 
.Ar service-name
parameters are typically
.Nm ssh
and
.Nm login .
